text: Stand Up Rahul is an 2022 Telugu-language coming of age romantic comedy film. It is written and directed by Santo Mohan Veeranki. It stars Raj Tarun, Varsha Bollamma, Murali Sharma, Indraja, and Vennela Kishore.https://www.outlookindia.com/art-entertainment/raj-tarun-starrer- stand-up-rahul-trailer-released-news-185201 It released on March 18, 2022 in theaters coinciding with the Holi festival. It is produced by Nandkumar Abbineni and Bharath Maguluri under the banner of Dream Town Productions and Highfive Pictures. The film's music was composed by Sweekar Agasthi. ==Plot== A feel-good romance comedy about a reluctant startup employee who doesn't stand up for anything in life, finally finding true love and learning to stand up for his parents, for his love and for his passion for stand-up comedy. ==Cast== *Raj Tarun as Rahul Dandapani *Varsha Bollamma as Sreya Rao *Murali Sharma as Prakash, Rahul's father *Indraja as Indu, Rahul's mother *Vennela Kishore as Steve Jags *Devi Prasad as Sreya's father *Rajkumar Kasireddy as Rahul's friend ==References== Category:2022 romantic comedy movies Category:2020s Indian movies
title: Stand Up Rahul
